{"tid":773174,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我係咪一路都ff緊？","createTime":"2018-08-09T10:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T07:49:38.000Z","uid":71508,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f41a8597377915e64c5f5a9bffb5eabbd32b6cb1","tid":773174,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"之前同女同學唔多熟啦 <br />\n前幾日同女同學進展都幾順利啦 <br />\n傾下電話facetime一齊出去補習等等啦 <br />\n補習之前仲行咗一陣街 <br />\n點知今日比個同班杯佢嘅女同學（肥婆）發現我同佢補習 <br />\n跟住寸鳩我 <br />\n咁我果下無經大腦思考就好緊張咁問佢點知啦..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但跟住見到女同學黑哂面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住就比女同學嘅private ig block咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有無機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係我一路都係隻兵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7d6fb68e30ac05361d575715039d437692cbce","tid":773174,"uid":19604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:19:42.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"7ac89f2faa33649559d984f5f2ea22e4381ff7dc","tid":773174,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b7d6fb68e30ac05361d575715039d437692cbce","tid":773174,"uid":19604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:19:42.000Z","msg":"55"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:21:39.000Z","msg":"你條毒撚妒忌我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796522ab3dd8e42ad8f18dc485983a4b040ef133","tid":773174,"uid":136449,"like":0,"dislike":0,